<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Reservation Request Received</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    h2 {
      color: #007bff;
    }
    .details {
      margin-top: 15px;
      background: #f1f1f1;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 25px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <h2>Reservation Request Received</h2>
    <p>Dear <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>

    <p>Thank you for choosing <strong>Café XYZ</strong>!</p>

    <p>We’ve received your reservation request and our team is currently reviewing it. You’ll receive a confirmation email shortly (within 10–15 minutes).</p>

    <div class="details">
      <p><strong>Reservation ID:</strong> <%= reservationID %></p>
      <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= date %></p>
      <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= time %></p>
      <p><strong>Number of People:</strong> <%= noOfPeople %></p>
    </div>

    <p>If you have any urgent queries, feel free to reply to this email or contact us directly.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      — Café XYZ<br/>
      📍 Main Street, Your City<br/>
      ☎️ 123-456-7890<br/>
      🌐 www.cafexyz.com
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
